OL,3,C'That's inhumane': New Zealand airport
OL,4,Cimposes three-minute hugging limit
OL,6,FA New Zealand airport has sparked
OL,7,Fcontroversy after imposing a three-
OL,8,Fminute limit on hugging in its drop-
OL,9,Foff zone.
OL,11,FDunedin Airport, located in the
OL,12,Fsouthern part of the country, has put
OL,13,Fup a warning sign that reads, "For
OL,14,Ffonder farewells please use the car
OL,15,Fpark."
