OL,3,C'That's inhumane': New Zealand airport
OL,4,Cimposes three-minute hugging limit
OL,6,FHe went on to describe airports as
OL,7,F"hotbeds of emotion," and mentioned a
OL,8,Fstudy which suggests a 20-second hug
OL,9,Fis enough to get a burst of the "love
OL,10,Fhormone" oxytocin.
OL,12,F"Our staff have seen some interesting
OL,13,Fthings over the years," he added.
OL,15,FBut the sign has caused controversy on
OL,16,Fsocial media with some labelling it as
OL,17,F"inhumane".
